# Assets Equity Securities Held Amount

## identifier
de13307

## type
float

## definition
This is equity securities held, which are contracts that evidence a residual interest in the assets of an entity after deducting all its liabilities. Securities are classified as debt or equity in accordance with the relevant accounting standards.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=Assets.EquitySecuritiesHeld.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo1.02.18
- period=instant
